query:
INSERT INTO fuel_stint_average_times AS fs
                    (plan_id,
                    lap_time,
                    fuel_per_lap,
                    lap_count,
                    lap_time_with_pit,
                    track_time,
                    track_time_with_pit,
                    fuel_per_stint,
                    stint_type)
                VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9)
                ON CONFLICT (plan_id, stint_type) DO UPDATE 
                SET 
                    lap_time = $2,
                    fuel_per_lap = $3,
                    lap_count = $4,
                    lap_time_with_pit = $5,
                    track_time = $6,
                    track_time_with_pit = $7,
                    fuel_per_stint = $8
                WHERE fs.plan_id = $1 AND fs.stint_type = $9
